near your car so you can hide from a storm if needed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/camping-iceland-car-tent.jpg\" alt=\"camping iceland car tent\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"camping iceland car tent\" class=\"wp-image-8169 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping-iceland-car-tent-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152902\/camping