up\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Food and water<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many supermarkets like Bonus and Kronan in the bigger cities. Remember that you have a single stove so try to cook basic. Dishes like pasta with vegetables and a sauce are very affordable. To save money, skip the meat and alcohol, those prices will force you to double or triple your budget.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/camping-iceland-cook.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"254\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8156\" class=\"wp-image-8156 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook-254x338.jpg 254w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook-450x600.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook-608x810.jpg 608w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook-122x163.jpg 122w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camping-iceland-cook-135x180.jpg 135w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152930\/camp