n tank. <\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7874&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152851\/guide-camping-iceland-pin.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152851\/guide-camping-iceland-pin-21x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152851\/guide-camping-iceland-pin-430x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Complete Guide to Camping in Iceland\" height=\"600\" width=\"430\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>At HappyCampers headquarters they have the free zone where travelers leave their groceries when they finished the trip. Take everything you need from this and save a lot of money.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\